# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:19
translate portuguese welchs1_b8887ab1:

    # pc "You were married?"
    pc "Foste casada?"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:24
translate portuguese welchmarried_c27601eb:

    # sst "Oh yeah. Right out of high school. Lasted about two years."
    sst "Sim. Logo a seguir ao liceu. Durou cerca de dois anos."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:25
translate portuguese welchmarried_d6a910a0:

    # sst "But he was controlling and emotionally abusive..."
    sst "Mas ele era controlador e emocionalmente abusivo..."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:27
translate portuguese welchmarried_6cf00ff4:

    # sst "So, I left his ass."
    sst "Por isso, mandei-o dar uma volta."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:29
translate portuguese welchmarried_5314674d:

    # sst "The whole thing made me stronger though. I don't think I'd be the same person today if I hadn't married that asshole."
    sst "No entanto, tudo isso tornou-me mais forte. Acho que não seria a mesma pessoa hoje se não tivesse casado com aquele idiota."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:31
translate portuguese welchmarried_a405651c:

    # sst "Plus, I got a pretty sweet house out of the divorce."
    sst "Além disso, fiquei com uma casa bem fixe no divórcio."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:32
translate portuguese welchmarried_7acc68d6:

    # pc "Hey, that's cool."
    pc "Ei, isso é fixe."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:34
translate portuguese welchmarried_5d0c7d8f:

    # sst "His parents and I always got along."
    sst "Os pais dele e eu sempre nos demos bem."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:35
translate portuguese welchmarried_c3bfaae0:

    # sst "They helped me a lot when I was leaving him, and we still go out for dinner once a month or so."
    sst "Eles ajudaram-me imenso quando o deixei, e ainda saímos para jantar uma vez por mês, mais ou menos."

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:37
translate portuguese welchmarried_9b93bf6c:

    # sst "So, I guess I took his family in the divorce too! Hah!"
    sst "Então, acho que fiquei com a família dele no divórcio também! Hah!"

